name: Studio Apartment at East Boston Pier Near Water
neighborhood_overview: The property is also less than a mile from the North End, Old North Church, Quincy Market, and Faneuil Hall.
description:
Executive Studio with Water and City Views in East Boston! This building boasts some of the nicest amenities in the city.
Dogs and cats allowed. Breed and weight restrictions may apply. A one-time, non-refundable pet fee of $300 is required per pet.

The space
Studio comes with full kitchen, housewares, linens, towels, in unit laundry, WiFi, cable, queen size bed and double sleeper sofa.

Guest access
The amenities on the first floor of the complex are all shared spaces: game room with billiards, lounge and fireplace.

Other things to note
Please note that this is an apartment community and the building is not affiliated with your reservation. The concierge and building management do not recognize AirBNB reservations so you must say Northeast Suites in order to gain access to the apartment.
